Please note: these Python files are OS.system('') Text Colour Driven.

After you download these Python files, simply 'Double-Click' the file's name and the nice, rich coloured text will appear.
Note: if you run the files in 'Python Idle'/programming mode, you will not be able to see the cool looking coloured text.

Experiment with these Python files and have fun exploring and learning what Python is truly all about...
